#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid "molded glaze"
msgid_plural "molded glaze"
msgstr[0] "成型釉料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'molded glaze', 'str_pl': 'molded glaze'}
#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid ""
"It is a molded glaze used for firing the glaze hammer. Steel exteriors are "
"damaged at launch and can not be reused."
msgstr "這是一種用於燒製釉錘的成型釉料。鋼製外殼在發射時受損，無法重複使用。"

#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid "iron electromagnetic projectile"
msgid_plural "iron electromagnetic projectiles"
msgstr[0] "鐵質電磁彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'iron electromagnetic projectile', 'str_pl':
#. 'iron electromagnetic projectiles'}
#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A rod for electromagnetic projectile guns made of iron. It is easy to make, "
"but it is fragile compared to other EM projectiles, so it lacks flight "
"distance and stability."
msgstr "一種由鐵製成的電磁彈射槍用彈杆。它易於製造，但與其他電磁彈相比較為脆弱，因此射程和穩定性不足。"

#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid "steel electromagnetic projectile"
msgid_plural "steel electromagnetic projectiles"
msgstr[0] "鋼質電磁彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel electromagnetic projectile', 'str_pl':
#. 'steel electromagnetic projectiles'}
#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A rod for electromagnetic projectile guns made of steel. It is a standard "
"projectile with stable performance."
msgstr "一種由鋼製成的電磁彈射槍用彈杆。它是一種性能穩定的標準彈體。"

#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid "superalloy electromagnetic projectile"
msgid_plural "superalloy electromagnetic projectiles"
msgstr[0] "超級合金電磁彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superalloy electromagnetic projectile',
#. 'str_pl': 'superalloy electromagnetic projectiles'}
#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A rod for electromagnetic projectile guns made of superalloy. It is a "
"projectile with high performance due to its excellent electrical and "
"chemical properties."
msgstr "一種由超級合金製成的電磁彈射槍用彈杆。由於其優異的電學和化學特性，它是一種高性能彈體。"

#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid "electromagnetic projectile magazine"
msgid_plural "electromagnetic projectile magazines"
msgstr[0] "電磁彈彈匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'electromagnetic projectile magazine', 'str_pl':
#. 'electromagnetic projectile magazines'}
#: .\cbma_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A magazine dedicated to the improved electromagnetic projectile gun. You can"
" load up to 20 rods."
msgstr "專為改進型電磁彈射槍設計的彈匣。最多可裝載20根彈杆。"

#: .\cbma_ammo_types.json
msgid "ammo pile"
msgstr "彈藥堆"

#: .\cbma_ammo_types.json
msgid "electromagnetic projectiles"
msgstr "電磁投射物"

