#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic armor (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective suit that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, this is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. The built-"
"in mechanism that is activated strengthens the cardiopulmonary function and "
"can exert greater power than usual."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護服，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。激活的內置機制強化了心肺功能，能夠發揮出比平常更強大的力量。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic helmet"
msgid_plural "bionic helmets"
msgstr[0] "仿生頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic helmet'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough, lightweight protective helmet that combines superalloys and Kevlar."
" It protects you firmly against physical factors."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護頭盔。它能為你提供堅實的物理防護。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic mask"
msgid_plural "bionic masks"
msgstr[0] "仿生面罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic mask'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough, lightweight protective mask that combines superalloys and Kevlar. "
"It protects you strongly from various environmental factors besides physical"
" factors."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護面罩。除了物理因素外，它還能強力保護你免受各種環境因素的影響。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic helmet (off)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic helmet (off)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生頭盔（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic helmet (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective helmet that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. By "
"activating various expansion systems installed inside, it is possible to "
"operate under various environments."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護頭盔，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。通過激活內部安裝的各種擴展系統，可以在各種環境下操作。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic helmet (on)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic helmet (on)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生頭盔（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic helmet (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective helmet that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. It operates "
"the built-in expansion system and is capable of aiming assistance, loud "
"protection, and underwater activities."
msgstr ""
"一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護頭盔，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。它運行內置的擴展系統，能夠提供瞄準輔助、噪音防護和水下活動支持。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic gloves"
msgid_plural "bionic glovess"
msgstr[0] "仿生手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic gloves'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A pair of superalloys and Kevlar combined with a strong, lightweight arm "
"covering the entire arm. It protects you firmly against physical factors."
msgstr "一副結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便護臂，覆蓋整個手臂。它能為你提供堅實的物理防護。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic gloves (off)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic gloves (off)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生手套（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic gloves (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight pair of superalloys and Kevlar combined with a "
"further improvement to the hand, this is a gem that should be called "
"Survivor Power Armor."
msgstr "一副結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便手套，對手部進行了進一步改進，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic gloves (on)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic gloves (on)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生手套（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic gloves (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight pair of superalloys and Kevlar combined with a "
"further improvement to the hand, this is a gem that should be called "
"Survivor Power Armor. The embedded electronic auxiliary system enables "
"accurate operation and does not disturb the operation at all."
msgstr ""
"一副結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便手套，對手部進行了進一步改進，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。嵌入的電子輔助系統實現了精確操作，完全不會干擾操作。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic boots"
msgid_plural "bionic bootss"
msgstr[0] "仿生靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic boots'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough, lightweight protective boot that combines superalloy and Kevlar. It"
" protects you firmly against physical factors."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護靴。它能為你提供堅實的物理防護。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic boots (off)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic boots (off)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生靴（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic boots (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective boot that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem to be called Survivor Power Armor. When activated, it "
"activates the lower limb operation support device."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護靴，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。激活時，它會啟動下肢操作支持裝置。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic boots (on)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic boots (on)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生靴（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic boots (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective boot that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. The lower-"
"limb aiding device is in operation and helps more accurate avoidance and "
"positioning."
msgstr "一種結合了超級合金與凱夫拉縴維的堅固輕便防護靴，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。下肢輔助裝置正在運行，有助於更精準的閃避和定位。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic duster"
msgid_plural "bionic dusters"
msgstr[0] "仿生防塵大衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic duster'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A carbon fiber and Kevlar composite coat for ease of movement and "
"accommodation."
msgstr "一件由碳纖維和凱夫拉複合材料製成的大衣，便於活動與適應。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic duster (off)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic duster (off)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生防塵大衣（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic duster (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A specially made coat that incorporates superalloy point armor and a whole-"
"body dielectric device into the bionic coat. By activating the dielectric "
"device, the wearer can be protected from electrical damage."
msgstr "一件特製大衣，將超級合金點狀裝甲和全身絕緣裝置融入仿生大衣中。通過啟動絕緣裝置，穿戴者可免受電擊傷害。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic duster (on)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic duster (on)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生防塵大衣（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic duster (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A specially made coat that incorporates superalloy point armor and a whole-"
"body dielectric device into the bionic coat. The dielectric device is "
"activated and can protect the wearer from electrical damage."
msgstr "一件特製大衣，將超級合金點狀裝甲和全身絕緣裝置融入仿生大衣中。絕緣裝置已激活，可保護穿戴者免受電擊傷害。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic transport frame (off)"
msgid_plural "bionic transport frame (off)s"
msgstr[0] "仿生運輸框架（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic transport frame (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"It is a modified version of the transport frame for Power Armor so that it "
"can be used alone. It is currently without power."
msgstr "這是動力裝甲運輸框架的改裝版本，以便單獨使用。目前未通電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "bionic transport frame (on)"
msgid_plural "bionic transport frame (on)s"
msgstr[0] "仿生運輸框架（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic transport frame (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"It is a modified version of the transport frame for Power Armor so that it "
"can be used alone."
msgstr "這是動力裝甲運輸框架的改裝版本，以便單獨使用。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "inner armored suit (off)"
msgid_plural "inner armored suit (off)s"
msgstr[0] "內置裝甲服（關閉）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inner armored suit (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A thin, strong Myamar inner suit covering the entire body. The artificial "
"muscles are not powered and do not perform as expected. Power supply is "
"started by starting up."
msgstr "一件覆蓋全身的輕薄而堅固的邁亞瑪內置服。人造肌肉未通電，無法發揮預期性能。通過啟動來開始供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "inner armored suit (on)"
msgid_plural "inner armored suit (on)s"
msgstr[0] "內置裝甲服（開啟）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inner armored suit (on)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A thin, strong Myamar inner suit covering the entire body. Electric power is"
" supplied to the artificial muscles, and the original performance is "
"exhibited."
msgstr "一件覆蓋全身的輕薄而堅固的邁亞瑪內置服。電力供應給人造肌肉，展現出原有性能。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic armor (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic armor (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生裝甲（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic armor (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective suit that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, this is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. Power for "
"normal operation is supplied by Solar and Ratchet. It has been modified so "
"that UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一套結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護服，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。正常運作的電力由太陽能和棘輪裝置供應。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic armor (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic armor (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生裝甲（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic armor (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective suit that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, this is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. The built-"
"in mechanism that is activated strengthens the cardiopulmonary function and "
"can exert greater power than usual. It has been modified so that the UPS can"
" supply power."
msgstr ""
"一套結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護服，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。激活的內置機制增強心肺功能，能發揮比平時更大的力量。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced helmet (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced helmet (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型頭盔（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced helmet (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective helmet that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. By "
"activating various expansion systems installed inside, it is possible to "
"operate under various environments. It has been modified so that the UPS can"
" supply power."
msgstr ""
"一頂結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護頭盔，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。通過激活內部安裝的各種擴展系統，可在多種環境下操作。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic helmet (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic helmet (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生頭盔（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic helmet (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective helmet that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. It operates "
"the built-in expansion system and is capable of aiming assistance, loud "
"protection, and underwater activities. It has been modified so that the UPS "
"can supply power."
msgstr ""
"一頂結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護頭盔，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。操作內置擴展系統，具備瞄準輔助、噪音防護和水下活動能力。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic gloves (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic gloves (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生手套（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic gloves (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight pair of superalloys and Kevlar combined with a "
"further improvement to the hand, this is a gem that should be called "
"Survivor Power Armor. It has been modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一雙結合超級合金和凱夫拉並進一步改進手部功能的堅韌輕便手套，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic gloves (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic gloves (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生手套（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic gloves (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight pair of superalloys and Kevlar combined with a "
"further improvement to the hand, this is a gem that should be called "
"Survivor Power Armor. The embedded electronic auxiliary system enables "
"accurate operation and does not disturb the operation at all. It has been "
"modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr ""
"一雙結合超級合金和凱夫拉並進一步改進手部功能的堅韌輕便手套，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。嵌入的電子輔助系統實現精確操作，完全不影響行動。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic boots (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic boots (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生靴（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic boots (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective boot that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. When "
"activated, it activates the lower limb operation support device. It has been"
" modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一雙結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護靴，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。激活時，啟動下肢操作支持裝置。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic boots (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic boots (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生靴（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic boots (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective boot that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, it is a gem to be called Survivor Power Armor. The lower-limb aiding"
" device is in operation and helps more accurate avoidance and positioning. "
"It has been modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一雙結合超級合金和凱夫拉的堅韌輕便防護靴，堪稱倖存者動力裝甲的瑰寶。下肢輔助裝置正在運行，幫助更精準的閃避和定位。已改裝以便UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic duster (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic duster (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生防塵大衣（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic duster (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A specially made coat that incorporates superalloy point armor and a whole-"
"body dielectric device into the bionic coat. By activating the dielectric "
"device, the wearer can be protected from electrical damage. It has been "
"modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一件特製大衣，將超合金點狀裝甲和全身絕緣裝置融入仿生大衣中。通過激活絕緣裝置，穿戴者可以免受電擊傷害。它經過改裝，可由UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic duster (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic duster (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "增強型仿生防塵大衣（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic duster (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A specially made coat that incorporates superalloy point armor and a whole-"
"body dielectric device into the bionic coat. The dielectric device is "
"activated and can protect the wearer from electrical damage. It has been "
"modified so that the UPS can supply power."
msgstr "一件特製大衣，將超合金點狀裝甲和全身絕緣裝置融入仿生大衣中。絕緣裝置已激活，可以保護穿戴者免受電擊傷害。它經過改裝，可由UPS供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "inner armored suit (off) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "inner armored suit (off) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "內置裝甲服（關閉）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inner armored suit (off) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A thin and strong inner cover made of Myamar fiber that covers the entire "
"body so that it can be fed by UPS. The artificial muscles are not powered "
"and do not perform as expected. Power supply is started by starting up."
msgstr "一件由邁亞瑪纖維製成的輕薄堅固內襯，覆蓋全身，可由UPS供電。人造肌肉未通電，無法發揮預期性能。通過啟動來開始供電。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "inner armored suit (on) (UPS)"
msgid_plural "inner armored suit (on) (UPS)s"
msgstr[0] "內置裝甲服（開啟）（UPS）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inner armored suit (on) (UPS)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A thin and strong inner cover made of Myamar fiber that covers the entire "
"body so that it can be fed by UPS. Electric power is supplied to the "
"artificial muscles, and the original performance is exhibited."
msgstr "一件由邁亞瑪纖維製成的輕薄堅固內襯，覆蓋全身，可由UPS供電。電力供應給人造肌肉，展現出原有性能。"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "EM railgun"
msgid_plural "EM railguns"
msgstr[0] "電磁軌道炮"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid ""
"A type of railgun that accelerates and ejects a projectile by "
"electromagnetic induction. The projectile to be ejected is semi-plasma and "
"can not be reused because it dissolves at the time of impact."
msgstr "一種通過電磁感應加速併發射彈丸的軌道炮。發射的彈丸為半等離子體，撞擊時會溶解，因此無法重複使用。"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "improved EM railgun"
msgid_plural "improved EM railguns"
msgstr[0] "改進型電磁軌道炮"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid ""
"A type of railgun that accelerates and ejects a projectile by "
"electromagnetic induction. The acceleration rail is shortened, and multiple "
"parallelization is provided with a pseudo blaze function. Also, because the "
"ammunition is made into a magazine, the time for reloading is shortened."
msgstr "一種通過電磁感應加速併發射彈丸的軌道炮。加速軌道縮短，並配備多重並行化及偽連發功能。此外，由於彈藥採用彈匣式，重新裝填時間縮短。"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "連發"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "explosive pile hammer"
msgid_plural "explosive pile hammers"
msgstr[0] "爆破樁錘"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid ""
"It is a weapon that shoots a superalloy 'pile' at a super high speed and "
"short distance by the explosive power of glaze loaded in the medicine room. "
"It's terribly embarrassing and bad, but you can see as many blows as there "
"is nothing to compare."
msgstr "這是一種利用藥室中裝載的釉藥爆炸力，在超高速和短距離內發射超合金“樁”的武器。它極其笨重且不便，但其打擊力無與倫比。"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "melee"
msgstr "近戰"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid "EM pile hammer"
msgid_plural "EM pile hammers"
msgstr[0] "電磁樁錘"

#: .\cbma_gun.json
msgid ""
"Instead of the explosive power of glaze, it is a weapon that shoots a "
"superalloy “pile” at an ultra-high speed and short distance by "
"electromagnetic induction. Although it consumes a great deal of power and is"
" less powerful than a glazed type, EMP generated by electromagnetic "
"induction can be expected to cause more damage to robots etc."
msgstr ""
"這是一種利用電磁感應而非釉藥爆炸力，在超高速和短距離內發射超合金“樁”的武器。雖然耗電量巨大且威力不如釉藥型，但電磁感應產生的EMP可對機器人等造成更多傷害。"

